pd_0_com_0text: And so, the play went on. It always would have, I suppose. Time marches ever onward and all that.
pd_0_com_1text: However, your efforts have had a noticeable effect on those folks up there, believe it or not. Why, if it wasn’t for you, they might not have gotten to this point at all.
pd_0_com_2text: Then again I guess you’ll never know. Unless you somehow begin this whole chain of events again, as preposterous as that is.
pd_0_com_3text: Oh, that reminds me, you have someone who seems to be saying goodbye. Any last words for her before she goes beyond?
pd_5_com_0text: Finer words were never spoken. And it seems the play has finished too. Congratulations, my friend, you’ve done it.
